criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. diagnosed with primary colorectal cancer;

          2. at least 20 years of age;

          3. able to read and speak Mandarin;

          4. own a smartphone and willingness to use the mobile app after discharge The exclusion
             criteria

        1.having other types of cancer; 2.having visual, hearing and/or cognitive
        impairments/mental disorders; 3.alcohol or drug abuse; 4.dying or having any surgical
        complications.
